Former Senator for Kaduna Central, Shehu Sani, has revealed that the national leader of the All Progressive Congress (APC), Asiwaju Ahmed Tinubu has sent out his congratulatory messages using envelopes. Recall that the Former Vice President Atiku Abubakar is being congratulated for winning the People’s Democratic Party (PDP) presidential ticket. However Sani in a tweet on Sunday, alleged that Jagaban as Tinubu popularly called sent his congratulations in some direct and indirect envelopes. -Advertisement- His tweet read, “Jagaban congratulatory messages was sent in direct and indirect envelopes.” Recall that APC, has postponed it’s presidential primary to June 6 to 8, as it was formerly scheduled for May 29 and 30, 2022.